 172}, {\"ngram\": \"the playoffs\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 188}, {\"ngram\": \"late April\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"early May\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an audacious goal, to have Team USA's men's basketball roster set with more than a month left in theNBA's postseason; it's too much time for a player Hill picked to be injured or otherwise tire out - especially considering theOlympicsare earlier this year and training camp begins in early July.\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.971528973252126e-15, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an audacious goal\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a month\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"theNBA's postseason\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"too much time\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"a player Hill\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsare\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"training camp\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"early July\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement When Hill (in conjunction with coach Steve Kerr and general manager Sean Ford) have the USA team set, apparently this spring, Hill said, \\\"There will be some people who are disappointed, who will not make that final 12 roster\\\" - an acknowledgement of the unprecedented pool of established NBA superstars, with unimpeachable international bona fides from past Team USA tours, mixed with younger, up-and-coming, American \\\"pipeline\\\" players who have expressed interest.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\