\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"physicality\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that leaves four more spots.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four more spots\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Past Olympic gold winnersJames Harden,Jrue Holiday,Kyrie Irving,Damian LillardandChris Paulhave all expressed interest.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrie_Irving\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kyrie Irving\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrie_Irving\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrie_Irving\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"winnersJames\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"Damian LillardandChris Paulhave\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Team USA deep thinkers took them too, we'd have a set American roster without a single player from the World Cup last summer or from an impressive mix of NBA veteran superstars (Kawhi Leonard) and up-and-coming stars (Desmond Bane,Chet Holmgren) on the team.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.971528973252126e-15, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.99179064623