 will be somebody we will consider,\\\" Hill said of Young.\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 6224, \"to\": 6232}, {\"ngram\": \"Hill\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6256}, {\"ngram\": \"Young\", \"from\": 6265, \"to\": 6270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But one thing I did tell him, and I will say this, I thought he was disappointed, obviously, last year, the fact that he was (so public about his disappointment) show a tremendous amount of courage.\", \"from\": 6272, \"to\": 6471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 6277, \"to\": 6286}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6385}, {\"ngram\": \"his disappointment\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6433}, {\"ngram\": \"a tremendous amount\", \"from\": 6440, \"to\": 6459}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 6463, \"to\": 6470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of guys might not be so public, and he was very honest about his disappointment.\", \"from\": 6472, \"to\": 6558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 6472, \"to\": 6477}, {\"ngram\": \"guys\", \"from\": 6481, \"to\": 6485}, {\"ngram\": \"his disappointment\", \"from\": 6539, \"to\": 6557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, so, that, in part, is why he's been so good.\", \"from\": 6559, \"to\": 6608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 6577, \"to\": 6581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's courageous, but we will see.\\\"\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Top photo: Alex Slitz / Getty Images) Spot the pattern.\", \"from\": 6645, \"to\": 6702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6657, \"end\": 6661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999987262821304, \"rank\": 8.286288452956016e-07, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"b